PortSystem 1.0
name		sobby
version		0.3.0
categories	x11 net
maintainers	pkern@opendarwin.org
description	Dedicated server for collaborative editing
homepage	http://darcs.0x539.de/trac/obby/
platforms	darwin freebsd

